formattedAddress: T2 Multi-User Domestic Terminal (Sydney (Kingsford Smith) Airport (SYD))
10/6 Cowper Wharf Roadway (btwn Bourke St. & Forbes St.)

tip.text: Delicious breakfast menu, and the staff aren't too hard to look at ;o) Eggs Bene with smoked salmon and chive hollandaise is awesome!
Yummy low caffeine tea, great gals behind the counter and a very cool vibe.
The Mordant Wing. They say God is in the detail. The atheists will be delighted with this building.
In to week 2; well on my way to my goal and feeling great!
